-- ds.page: Section Syntax

Section definition syntax, nesting rules, and component invocations in FTD

-- ds.h1: Basic Section Syntax

A section in FTD starts with `--` followed by the section name.

-- ds.code: Basic Sections
lang: ftd

\-- ftd.text: Hello World
\-- component-name: Component with caption

-- ds.h1: Section Nesting

Sections can contain nested child sections using indentation.